properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 15 at 1:46PM PST until January 16 at 9:00PM PST by NWS Las Vegas NV
properties.description:
* WHAT...South winds 20 to 30 mph with gusts 40 to 50 mph
expected.

* WHERE...In Nevada, Esmeralda and Central Nye County and
Western Clark and Southern Nye County. In California, Owens
Valley, White Mountains of Inyo County and Death Valley
National Park.

* WHEN...From 10 AM to 9 PM PST Thursday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds can make driving difficult...especially
for high profile vehicles. Gusty winds could blow around
unsecured objects.
properties.instruction:
Drivers of motorcycles...vans...campers...trailers...and other
high profile vehicles should be alert to the danger of these
winds. Use extra caution. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT FROM 10 AM TO 9 PM PST THURSDAY
